        h2.liposuction__title.c-title.c-title--center INTRODUCTION
        p.liposuction__desc.c-desc!= "At our practice in <strong>New York City, liposuction</strong> surgery is a very popular procedure. Liposuction, which is commonly referred to as “lipo,” is a procedure that removes fat deposits from specific areas of the body. Liposuction can also help the body appear more contoured and more proportionate."
        p.liposuction__desc.c-desc!= "Dr. Lao strives to deliver the <strong>best liposuction New York, NY</strong> residents can look forward to. He places patient safety and communication as his top priorities."

