    .c-grid
      .liposuction__wrapper.liposuction__wrapper-2
        div
          h3.liposuction__subtitle.c-title.c-title--medium WHY LIPOSUCTION?
          p.liposuction__desc.c-desc!= "Liposuction is one of the most useful tools used by <span>Dr. Lao</span> in aesthetic and reconstructive <span>plastic surgery</span>. Not only is it used to <span>extract fat</span> for the purpose of fat injection, strategic extraction of fat in certain areas can also obtain the desired body curve. It is also used in conjunction with other <span>body contouring procedures</span> like <span>abdominoplasty (tummy tuck)</span>, brachioplasty (arm lift), thighplasty (thigh lift) procedures to perfect their results."

          h3.liposuction__subtitle.c-title.c-title--medium WHO IS A GOOD CANDIDATE FOR LIPOSUCTION?
          p.liposuction__desc.c-desc Men and women who live a healthy lifestyle, are at a stable weight and have elastic skin are typically good candidates for liposuction. Individuals who have fat deposits that won’t go away with diet and exercise are also excellent candidates for this procedure.
          p.liposuction__desc.c-desc!= "We ask that any candidates who come to see us for <strong>liposuction in NYC</strong> have realistic expectations of what the procedure can and cannot do."

